s/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3447a0ffaacc94f548fbe00621d7a7a112e04fe","tid":1994711,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c7a7bb9a8650a067203877ddd373548dd2e79f2","tid":1994711,"uid":71824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:29:48.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n紋朵花都難接受啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:40:56.000Z","msg":"唐朝貴妃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5710adf697ce9a3da879e83070f88e45cb57a80","tid":1994711,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:42:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d36d3924e3cc9f9be1c79c53371b4d61af7c53e","tid":1994711,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"天眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c70f620ad05f98fead58cd4f2b8907a57678c4f","tid":1994711,"uid":30601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:45:52.000Z","msg":"佢畫上個面個稿同完成品都差好遠啦，點估到會畫到花成咁阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92014a1c1df3c4beaf417be0c0491d2e51ad30ea","tid":1994711,"uid":243106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"有啲似小朋友亂畫落幅牆咁"},{"pid":"4fbc3773e2b37605b6cd96c92056379cf07cf137","tid":1994711,"uid":64542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T17:10:36.000Z","msg":"口罩倒轉帶，個人精神晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6107a1cbb5080cbd076b8d5b156d7dc72557831f","tid":1994711,"uid":10503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T17:14:16.000Z","msg":"俾人headshot咁"},{"pid":"bc5851d263e309a6aeac28dc43d682d8e32e6955","tid":1994711,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T17:15:46.000Z","msg":"屎眼加啲閪毛"},{"pid":"37009fc499baa377773a7c0a12093c5b6fa743fb","tid":1994711,"uid":28031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"對比圖睇得出個客試過染髮同眉去嘗試carry個紋身，應該係試完carry唔掂先出黎屌鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61bc048ebd66b95a4493a62f5bfc465d9febc46d","tid":1994711,"uid":207149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T19:11:05.000Z","msg":"柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea25e59debb79fecc40ebea23f2bbe8da10b857c","tid":1994711,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T20:28:22.000Z","msg":"紋身 = 污糟邋遢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236857a0e5e0a89bbf18443321eba518a62368a5","tid":1994711,"uid":355659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T21:12:31.000Z","msg":"點樣可以喺無客人同意情況下紋到個額頭咁樣，似係個客事後反悔多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104515ee2ea527ffe75d280992b2fc4a377dc7b6","tid":1994711,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T23:12:48.000Z","msg":"紋個閪喺額頭做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}